channel.title: Need help with Silab NPC's
channel.description: umm... yeah i need help with adding silab npc's to my server. If i add the id to npc.cfg and spawn it with autospawn, sometimes its a different npc with a different id, or sometimes its an object. For example, i'm working on a god wars dungeon atm and if i try to spawn a zamorak mage, it spawns a wandering camper.
